# Bark & Bite - Iranian APT Detection Rules: March 2026 Update
# Version: 3.0
# Last Updated: 2026-03-09
# Credit: Bark & Bite Security
#
# This update covers new Iranian APT activity from July 2025 through March 2026.
# Designed to append to the existing base rules (SID 2000001-2000130).
# New SID range: 2000131-2000230
#
# Threat context: Following the June 2025 twelve-day Iran-Israel war and
# Operation Epic Fury (Feb 28, 2026), Iranian cyber operations are at their
# highest-ever tempo. MuddyWater, CyberAv3ngers, UNC1549, Infy, and
# RedKitten are all actively targeting U.S. and Western critical infrastructure.
#
# References:
#   - CISA Joint Fact Sheet: Iranian Cyber Actors May Target Vulnerable US
